14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
16 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
17 A. There is hereby appropriated to the County Improvements for
18 Roads and Bridges Fund created pursuant to Section 507 of Title 69
19 of the Oklahoma Statutes from any monies not otherwise appropriated
20 from the General Revenue Fund of the State Treasury for the fiscal
21 year ending June 30, 2026, the sum of Twenty-five Million Dollars
22 ($25,000,000.00) or so much thereof as may be necessary for the
23 reconstruction of county bridges on the portion of the county
24 highway system defined as Major Collector routes in accordance with
